zt820 is a nice irc eggdrop robot written in C.

In future zt820 will:
- talk with you,
- have feelings and act according,
- help you doing:
  - math calculations,
  - browse google,
  - browse feeds,


*INSTALL*

$ ./autogen.sh

# check dependencies and make build on Linux
$ ./configure

# OSX
$ ./configure --enable-openssl=/usr/local/opt/openssl

# compile code
$ make


*RUN*

$ ./src/zt820


*TEST AND INSTALL*
# if you wanna test things
$ make test

# install on system
$ sudo make install DESTDIR=/usr


*EDIT CONFIGURATION FILE*
$ vim data/config
